<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5811] The Overseer will retry work items until success.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5811</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This means that if you get a bad item in the ZK distributed queue, it can lock up your Overseer as it continuously retries the bad command. The workaround is to manually clear the Overseer ZK queue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
